    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You've honestly gotta see this beauty in person. It is in absolutely pristine, showroom condition\u2014I've babied it since day one and there isn't a single scratch to be found! It drives like a dream and basically feels brand new. If you're looking for that perfect 'new car' experience without the dealership headache, this is the one for you. Let's get you behind the wheel!",
      "price": 44500.0,
