      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive preservation. This vehicle remains in showroom condition, having been meticulously garage-kept and climate-controlled since its initial purchase. The exterior finish retains its deep, factory luster with absolutely no swirl marks, stone chips, or imperfections to speak of. Inside, the cabin is indistinguishable from new; the premium leather upholstery remains supple without a single crease, and the original protective films are still present on several interior components. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, benefiting from a rigorous maintenance schedule performed exclusively by certified technicians. Every button, sensor, and feature functions precisely as intended. Complete with all original keys, manuals, and a comprehensive service history, this is a rare opportunity for the discerning collector or enthusiast who demands nothing less than perfection.",
      "price": 46500.0,
